content:
You can now use custom fiscal forecasts in Revenue Insights. 

This change applies to Sales Cloud in Lightning Experience in Enterprise and Unlimited editions for an additional cost.

To use this feature, enable custom fiscal year usage in Data Prep. From Analytics Object Manager, go to Data Prep Settings, and click Enable Date Settings.

Let us know if this solved your issue so we can improve!
title: Custom Fiscal Forecasts in Salesforce Revenue Insights
